# theHarvester #

"These are my notes on theHarvester tool used for information gathering."
--> What is theHarvester?

theHarvester is an OSINT (Open Source Intelligence) tool used to collect publicly available information about a target.

--> Information Collected

- Email Addresses
- Subdomains
- Host Names
- IP Addresses

--> Basic Command

theHarvester -d <domain> -b google

-d = Specifies the target domain.

-b = Specifies the data source (google, bing, yahoo, etc.).

--> Example

theHarvester -d example.com -b google

--> Uses

- Information Gathering
- Footprinting
- Reconnaissance
